---
---
<section class="bg-[#cafdd4] py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-7xl h-full opacity-5 pointer-events-none">
        <span class="text-[30rem] font-headline font-black uppercase italic leading-none whitespace-nowrap">QUIBDÓ 2024</span>
    </div>
    <div class="px-8 md:px-24 relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                <h2 class="text-5xl font-headline font-black uppercase tracking-tighter italic text-[#006b1b]">Próxima Gran Cita</h2>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold text-[#4252b4] mt-2">CAMPEONATO DEPARTAMENTAL DE VELOCIDAD</h3>
                <p class="mt-6 text-[#3b6447] text-lg max-w-md">La élite del atletismo chocoano se reúne en la capital para definir quién es el más veloz de la región.</p>
                <div class="mt-12 flex gap-4 md:gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-[#acecbb] p-6 min-w-[100px] text-center rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                        <span class="block text-4xl font-headline font-black text-[#006b1b]">12</span>
                        <span class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-[#3b6447]">Días</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-[#acecbb] p-6 min-w-[100px] text-center rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                        <span class="block text-4xl font-headline font-black text-[#006b1b]">08</span>
                        <span class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-[#3b6447]">Horas</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-[#acecbb] p-6 min-w-[100px] text-center rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                        <span class="block text-4xl font-headline font-black text-[#006b1b]">45</span>
                        <span class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-[#3b6447]">Min</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 space-y-4 shadow-xl -rotate-2 rounded-xl">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[#6c5a00]">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">calendar_month</span>
                        <span class="font-bold">24 de Agosto</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="font-headline font-black text-xl uppercase italic">Categoría Abierta</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#3b6447]">Estadio "La Normal" - Quibdó</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#006b1b] text-[#d1ffc8] p-8 space-y-4 shadow-xl rotate-1 rounded-xl">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">group</span>
                        <span class="font-bold">500+ Atletas</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="font-headline font-black text-xl uppercase italic">Todas las edades</p>
                    <button class="w-full bg-[#fdd835] text-[#5b4b00] py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase rounded-lg">Registrarse</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
